data.description: Get ready to call this fresh and unique bungalow HOME!  Located in a quiet neighborhood close to everything Hermitage has to offer, this 3 bedroom, 1 gorgeous bathroom  home is move-in ready.  Brand new flooring in the living room meets up with a recently updated kitchen.  You'll love the coffee nook, island and farm house sink. Walk down the hall to your new bathroom with modern walk in shower!   Finish off the main floor with a nice sized bedroom.   Make your way to the upper level and find 2 more nice sized bedrooms.  Head to the lower level laundry/ additional living space.  Ready to head outside?  The enclosed side porch leads to your huge back garage and inviting covered patio.  With just enough back yard to relax and play this property is perfect for entertaining.
